%% Gambar IV.2 - SSD request REST
%% Type: System Sequence Diagram.
%% Reference basis: Larman for SSD; UML 2.5.1 sequence diagram; RFC 9110.
sequenceDiagram
    actor VU as k6 virtual user
    participant REST as APE REST system
    participant DAL as Shared DAL
    participant DB as SQLite corpus

    VU->>REST: GET /images/{id}/detections?fields=&class_id=&min_confidence=
    REST->>DAL: get_image_with_detections(image_id, filters)
    DAL->>DB: SELECT image and detection rows
    DB-->>DAL: rows
    DAL-->>REST: image envelope + detections
    REST->>REST: project fields and compute cache headers
    REST-->>VU: 200 JSON + Cache-Control/ETag + X-Process-Time

